#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.sample.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.sample"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:1 of
msgid "Return a random sample of items from an axis of object."
msgstr "从对象的某个轴返回随机样本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:3 of
msgid "You can use `random_state` for reproducibility."
msgstr "您可以使用 `random_state` 来保证结果的可重现性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:5 of
msgid ""
"Number of items from axis to return. Cannot be used with `frac`. Default "
"= 1 if `frac` = None."
msgstr ""
"要从轴返回的项目数量。不能与 `frac` 同时使用。如果 `frac` 为 None，则"
"默认值为 1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:8 of
msgid "Fraction of axis items to return. Cannot be used with `n`."
msgstr "要返回的轴项目的比例。不能与 `n` 同时使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:10 of
msgid "Allow or disallow sampling of the same row more than once."
msgstr "是否允许同一行被多次采样。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:12 of
msgid ""
"Default 'None' results in equal probability weighting. If passed a "
"Series, will align with target object on index. Index values in weights "
"not found in sampled object will be ignored and index values in sampled "
"object not in weights will be assigned weights of zero. If called on a "
"DataFrame, will accept the name of a column when axis = 0. Unless weights"
" are a Series, weights must be same length as axis being sampled. If "
"weights do not sum to 1, they will be normalized to sum to 1. Missing "
"values in the weights column will be treated as zero. Infinite values not"
" allowed."
msgstr ""
"默认值 'None' 表示等概率加权。如果传入的是 Series，将根据索引与目标对象"
"对齐。权重中存在但样本对象中不存在的索引值将被忽略，样本对象中存在但权重"
"中不存在的索引值将被赋予零权重。如果在 DataFrame 上调用，当 axis = 0 时"
"可以接受列名。除非权重是 Series，否则权重必须与所采样轴长度一致。如果权重"
"之和不为 1，它们将被归一化为总和为 1。权重列中的缺失值将被视为零。不允许"
"出现无穷值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:25 of
msgid ""
"If int, array-like, or BitGenerator (NumPy>=1.17), seed for random number"
" generator If np.random.RandomState, use as numpy RandomState object."
msgstr ""
"如果是 int、array-like 或 BitGenerator（NumPy>=1.17），则作为随机数生成器"
"的种子；如果是 np.random.RandomState，则直接用作 numpy 的 RandomState "
"对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:29 of
msgid ""
"Axis to sample. Accepts axis number or name. Default is stat axis for "
"given data type (0 for Series and DataFrames)."
msgstr ""
"要采样的轴。接受轴编号或名称。默认为给定数据类型的统计轴（Series 和 "
"DataFrame 为 0）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:32 of
msgid ""
"If True, always treat distribution of sample counts between data chunks "
"as multinomial distribution. This will accelerate sampling when data is "
"huge, but may affect randomness of samples when number of instances is "
"not very large."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，始终将数据块之间的样本计数分布视为多项分布。这在数据量很大"
"时会加速采样，但在实例数量不是很大时可能会影响样本的随机性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:38 of
msgid ""
"A new object of same type as caller containing `n` items randomly sampled"
" from the caller object."
msgstr "一个新的与调用者类型相同且包含从调用者对象中随机采样的 `n` 项的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:44 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrameGroupBy.sample`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:45 of
msgid "Generates random samples from each group of a DataFrame object."
msgstr "从 DataFrame 对象的每个组中生成随机样本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:47 of
msgid ":py:obj:`SeriesGroupBy.sample`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:48 of
msgid "Generates random samples from each group of a Series object."
msgstr "从 Series 对象的每个组中生成随机样本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:50 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.random.choice`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:51 of
msgid "Generates a random sample from a given 1-D numpy array."
msgstr "从给定的一维 numpy 数组中生成随机样本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:54 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:55 of
msgid "If `frac` > 1, `replacement` should be set to `True`."
msgstr "如果 `frac` > 1，应将 `replacement` 设置为 `True`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:58 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:71 of
msgid ""
"Extract 3 random elements from the ``Series`` ``df['num_legs']``: Note "
"that we use `random_state` to ensure the reproducibility of the examples."
msgstr ""
"从 ``Series`` ``df['num_legs']`` 中提取 3 个随机元素：注意我们使用 `"
"random_state` 来确保示例的可重现性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:81 of
#, python-format
msgid "A random 50% sample of the ``DataFrame`` with replacement:"
msgstr "带有放回的 ``DataFrame`` 的 50% 随机样本："

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:88 of
msgid ""
"An upsample sample of the ``DataFrame`` with replacement: Note that "
"`replace` parameter has to be `True` for `frac` parameter > 1."
msgstr ""
"带有放回的 ``DataFrame`` 上采样样本：注意当 `frac` 参数大于 1 时，`"
"replace` 参数必须为 `True`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.sample.sample:102 of
msgid ""
"Using a DataFrame column as weights. Rows with larger value in the "
"`num_specimen_seen` column are more likely to be sampled."
msgstr ""
"使用 DataFrame 的一列作为权重。在 `num_specimen_seen` 列中值较大的行更有"
"可能被采样。"

